    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Poppy Toast is an Action Arcade game about escaping the notorious Razzle HQ and bringing Poppy Toast to the world whilst avoiding Razzle's advanced block defence system. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791400/extras/4913dc6784a071aff13780b4d4fd93a3.avif?t=1733033096\" width=460 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience fast-paced toasty clicking action to pop your toast beyond the Razzle Blocks! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791400/extras/f49bf38988d4f52ba6d474937a1d2757.poster.avif?t=1733033096\" width=536 height=948 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791400/extras/f49bf38988d4f52ba6d474937a1d2757.webm?t=1733033096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791400/extras/f49bf38988d4f52ba6d474937a1d2757.mp4?t=1733033096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn points for every obstacle that you avoid and unlock new toast skins to escape with! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791400/extras/b028f27c3065449f3c701e56fc70643d.poster.avif?t=1733033096\" width=530 height=860 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791400/extras/b028f27c3065449f3c701e56fc70643d.webm?t=1733033096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791400/extras/b028f27c3065449f3c701e56fc70643d.mp4?t=1733033096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more points you accumulate, the more RGB there is. RGB is love, RGB is life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791400/extras/fe2dd0a955f5b77c3cd97ca3f4ed3b00.poster.avif?t=1733033096\" width=536 height=948 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791400/extras/fe2dd0a955f5b77c3cd97ca3f4ed3b00.webm?t=1733033096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791400/extras/fe2dd0a955f5b77c3cd97ca3f4ed3b00.mp4?t=1733033096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn the most points and obtain bragging rights atop the Steam Leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
